                            "26": {
                              "id": "26",
                              "speaker": "Shadowheart",
                              "text": "Those signs we found, about Dark Justiciars... perhaps they were no coincidence. In either case, I need to watch for any place dedicated to Lady Shar. A temple, perhaps.",
